## [Discussion](/documentation/AuthenticationServices/ASAuthorizationProviderExtensionLoginConfiguration/loginRequestHPKEPreSharedKeyID#discussion)

The PreSharedKey Id to be used for HPKE PSK for embedded login assertions. This is required if the loginRequestHPKEPreSharedKey is set.
